{"tid":1664320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞手足：不論你在哪裡出生，只要愛香港，就是香港人","createTime":"2019-10-20T04:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T06:24:41.000Z","uid":104902,"like":123,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b3cbab16da31cd2d37a4077d36d1570f50160056","tid":1664320,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"From立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n【1200】尖沙咀重慶大廈外，有南亞裔人士傳遞冰凍蒸餾水，準備稍後派發予遊行人士<br />\n<br />\n相關專題：【專題】不分膚色界限的抗爭前線 被捕「南亞手足」：終於覺得我都係香港人（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2MU0p5K）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MU0p5K%EF%BC%89&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc6npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=801cfebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2MU0p5K）</a><br />\n<br />\n// 「因為這裡是我們屋企。上一代會話鄉下係印度、巴基斯坦，但我啲朋友會話，我鄉下係紅磡、土瓜灣，我們的歸屬感、未來都在這裡。」少數族裔社工阿齊說，上一代不太支持示威，覺得不要多生事端「破壞社會」，但年輕一代多在香港受教育，「我們明白香港好特別，有言論自由。明天華裔失去了權利，我們的權利也一樣受影響。」少數族裔參與和理非遊行時，有華裔多謝他們支持。「他們覺得很奇怪，為什麼要多謝他們。他們會回應說，我們也是香港人啊！香港人、加油！他們同華裔一起嗌口號。」張說。運動至今近四個月，現在華裔在遊行時見到少數族裔不再覺得奇怪，「大家互相幫助，很融洽。」<br />\n<br />\n阿齊說，因今天的遊行沒有不反對通知書，許多朋友不敢參與遊行，但不少人會一起在重慶大廈門口派水，與「華裔手足」同行。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「不論你在哪裡出生，只要愛香港，就是香港人。So we need to stand together, as Hongkonger.」</span></span>//<br />\n<br />\nWe connected<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c2329303ced9aa8e6e473ba4621e69075da088","tid":1664320,"uid":18220,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:22:03.000Z","msg":"本地岀世香港人表示佢地就係我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地就係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec2d5a56b87ff66e51493ffc3ef53d07b1f2fcd","tid":1664320,"uid":176313,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:24:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以後香港人不分種族不分國籍，只問心！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9b6ca6a28489b116ac6d4b6e30779926bfa1b544","tid":1664320,"uid":105546,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"真係學到好多野<br />\n就算唔同膚色<br />\n或者攞左幾年香港身份證嘅都可以係香港人<br />\n<br />\n相反啲廢老係香港出世左咁多年都唔撚知自己有幾幸福"},{"pid":"6caae941f8cfe6a8847290df732c964abbd151b7","tid":1664320,"uid":104902,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a6c2329303ced9aa8e6e473ba4621e69075da088","tid":1664320,"uid":18220,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:22:03.000Z","msg":"本地岀世香港人表示佢地就係我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地就係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:24:45.000Z","msg":"岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />We are all Hongkongers!!!"},{"pid":"a70ad878ad9d00d4bfb30885a204e4aadcb8a5d9","tid":1664320,"uid":182406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:24:50.000Z","msg":"好感動"},{"pid":"6444c0e3c72ba8f087ce29e59f2ffaac0a1908d6","tid":1664320,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec5abcdd28e9c9101af6c6f2aa5f55c1f56ea8f","tid":1664320,"uid":235769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"我鄉下係葵芳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d74fbe254bcfcdb3967ff6d53a5e3a17d06a8b","tid":1664320,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:26:09.000Z","msg":"ever part of us, bro!"},{"pid":"dca8f7c4c402d62fabd15e23a6c33ecdf20d2101","tid":1664320,"uid":30453,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"ci